nodes.text: The Pixelito Puppeteers Union was a union of entertainers and puppeteers working in the city of Pixelito on Malastare.

One of their members was Xucaabo, who was a well-renowned and talented puppeteer. However, he was secretly a member Sebolto's drug cartel and was deeply in debt. For these reasons, he was wanted by Ask Aak. The bounty was claimed by Jango Fett in 32 BBY.
